{"tid":1902311,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"新冠肺炎︰高官減薪一月  醫護獲特別獎金","createTime":"2020-02-28T09:24:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T10:28:10.000Z","uid":141060,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fa73b0ce1e344e833d16e3bf17b10797dd7bc944","tid":1902311,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T09:24:43.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎︰高官減薪一月  醫護獲特別獎金<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200228/bkn-20200228160513262-0228_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20200228%2Fbkn-20200228160513262-0228_00912_001.html&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJD2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=1c8e96af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200228/bkn-20200228160513262-0228_00912_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新加坡新冠肺炎疫情嚴重，副總理兼財政部長王瑞傑周五（28日）宣布，為了共度時艱，所有內閣官員、政務官，以至總統哈莉瑪都會減薪一個月。而衞生部及醫護等前線抗疫人員，則可獲一個月的特別獎金。<br />\n<br />\n王瑞傑周五在國會總結新會計年度政府財政政策的辯論上，公布上述措施。除了閣員和政務官減薪，其他高級公務員亦將減薪半個月；國會議員則減少一個月的津貼。王瑞杰強調，此舉是為了展現新加坡的團結，政治領導應盡其所能幫助社會，幫助新加坡度過難關。<br />\n<br />\n衞生部、醫院醫護及其他前線抗疫公務員，均可獲得特別獎金。王瑞傑表示若有必要，會請示哈莉瑪，以便動用國家儲備金。他又指，「前線醫護人員每天都為未知的戰爭作犧牲」，形容有關措施是政府對他們最實際的支持。"},{"pid":"ad9e60ee941a05377cd610a5290c051d84a82c3b","tid":1902311,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T09:25:25.000Z","msg":"香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d3f218ebd1b1187e7421b8ebf76a993649893a","tid":1902311,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T09:25:32.000Z","msg":"相較之下，你睇下香港班高官 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入 －－》<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJD2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=bbb85db0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task</span></strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"6fa86ad72cb45130f8bfb5d338a52e591f7462ff","tid":1902311,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T10:22:42.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"482e005404be5d01d24c0aa4d3603000324e7867","tid":1902311,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad9e60ee941a05377cd610a5290c051d84a82c3b","tid":1902311,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T09:25:25.000Z","msg":"香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T10:23:59.000Z","msg":"睬你都on9"},{"pid":"acf2168c6eec807541852006e773e7297e265a81","tid":1902311,"uid":345137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T10:28:10.000Z","msg":"<strong>香港班官係對共產黨負責, 唔係香港人</strong><br />\n香港人同醫護係生係死WFC. <br />\n為左支共政治睇住香港人死都唔封關"}]}